<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>School Management System</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      color: white;
    }

    .container img {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #00d4ff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .buttons {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .login-btn,
    .guest-btn {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      margin: 5px;
    }

    .login-btn {
      background-color: #00d4ff;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .login-btn:hover {
      background-color: #009dcf;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px #00d4ff;
    }

    .guest-btn {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .guest-btn:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px #ccc;
    }

    .signup {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .signup a {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .signup a:hover {
      color: #00d4ff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="image/sms.jpg" alt="School Illustration">
    <h1>Welcome to <br>School Management System</h1>
    <p>Streamline school management, class organization, and add students and faculty. Seamlessly track attendance, assess performance, and provide feedback. Access records, view marks, and communicate effortlessly.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <button class="login-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/choose'">Login</button>

    </div>
    <p class="signup">Donâ€™t have an account? <a href="/signup">Sign up</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
